n===Class of 2013===\n* [[Gary Blair]]\n* [[Jim Foster (basketball)|Jim Foster]]\n* [[Peggie Gillom-Granderson]]\n* [[Jennifer Rizzotti]]\n* [[Annette Smith-Knight]]\n* [[Sue Wicks]]\n\n===Class of 2014===\n* [[Lin Dunn]]\n* [[Michelle Edwards (basketball)|Michelle Edwards]]\n* [[Mimi Griffin]]\n* [[Yolanda Griffith]]\n* [[Jasmina Perazi\u0107]]\n* [[Charlotte West (basketball)|Charlotte West]]\n\n===Class of 2015===\n* [[Janeth Arcain]]\n* [[Kurt Budke]]\n* [[Gail Goestenkors]]\n* [[Janet Harris]]\n* [[Lisa Leslie]]\n* [[Brad Smith (basketball)|Brad Smith]]\n\n===Class of 2016===\n* [[Sherri Coale]]\n* [[June Courteau]]\n* [[Joe Lombard]]\n* [[Jackie Stiles]]\n* [[Bill Tipps]]\n* [[Natalie Williams]]\n\n===Class of 2017===\n* [[Sally Bell]]\n* [[Christine Grant]]\n* [[Rick Insell]]\n* [[Louise O'Neal]]\n* [[Sheryl Swoopes]]\n* [[Kara Wolters]]\n\n===Class of 2018===\n* [[Ceal Barry]]\n* [[Rose Marie Battaglia]]\n* [[Chris Dailey]]\n* [[Mickie DeMoss]]\n* [[Liz Galloway McQuitter]]\n* [[Chamique Holdsclaw]]\n* [[Katie Smith]]\n* [[Tina Thompson]]\n\n===Class of 2019===\n* [[Beth Bass]]\n* [[Carolyn Bush Roddy]]\n* [[Joan Cronan]]\n* [[Nora Lynn Finch]]\n* [[Ticha Penicheiro]]\n* [[Ruth Riley]]\n* [[Valerie Still]]\n\n===Class of 2020===\n* [[Debbie Brock]]\n* [[Carol Callan]]\n* [[Swin Cash]]\n* [[Tamika Catchings]]\n* [[Sue Donohoe]]\n* [[Lauren Jackson]]\n* [[Carol Stiff]]\n\n==See also==\n\n* [[List of sports awards honoring women]]\n* [[List of members of the Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame]]\n** [[List of players in the Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame]]\n** [[List of coaches in the Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame]]\n* [[FIBA Hall of Fame]]\n** [[List of members of the FIBA Hall of Fame]]\n* [[International Women's Sports Hall of Fame]]\n* [[Women's Basketball Coaches Association]]\n\n==References==\n<references />\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.wbhof.com/ Women's Basketball Hall of Fame]\n* [http://www.wbhof.com/hall-of-famer